description.en:
Floki Musk is the youngest member of the Musk family and in honor of that, the Floki Musk token was born.
 
Total supply: 1,000,000,000,000 
100% Of Initial liquidity provided by team
Contract has no owner
No fees 
No burn
No presale
No team tokens
Liquidity locked

June 25: Elon tweeted that he will name his Shiba Inu Floki
September 13: Floki Musk was introduced by Elon to the world.
September 15: Floki Musk token was released 

For all the tesla & elon fans for all the doge & shiba inu lovers 

Nothing but a meme
The way it should be
